<p>ã“ã®è€ƒãˆæ–¹ã«ã¯ã€é‹å‹•ã™ã‚‹æ’æ˜Ÿã©ã†ã—ã®é‡åŠ›ç›¸äº’ä½œç”¨ãŒå«ã¾ã‚Œã¦ãŠã‚‰ãšã€ã¾ãŸæ¸¦çŠ¶è…•ãŒã§ããŸã“ã¨ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹éè»¸å¯¾ç§°æ€§ãŒè€ƒæ…®ã•ã‚Œã¦ã„ã¾ã›ã‚“ã€‚
ã“ã®ã“ã¨ã‹ã‚‰æ’æ˜Ÿã®è»Œé“é‹å‹•ã‹ã‚‰ä½œã‚‰ã‚ŒãŸå¯†åº¦æ³¢ã‚’ã€é‹å‹•å­¦çš„å¯†åº¦æ³¢ã¨å‘¼ã³ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã¾ãŸã€ã“ã“ã§ã¯\(\Omega_p\)ã‚’åŠå¾„ã«ã‚ˆã‚‰ãšã«ä¸€å®šã¨ã—ã¦ã„ã¾ã™ã€‚
å®Ÿéš›ã®éŠ€æ²³ã§ã¯\(\Omega_p\)ãŒåŠå¾„ã«ä¾å­˜ã—ã€æ¥•å††è»Œé“ã®é•·è»¸æ–¹å‘ã¯æ™‚äº‹åˆ»ã€…ã¨ãã®å‘ãã‚’å¤‰ãˆã¦ã„ããŸã‚ã€æ¸¦çŠ¶è…•ãŒå´©ã‚Œã¦ã„ãã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã®ã“ã¨ã‹ã‚‰ã‚‚ã“ã®èª¬æ˜ã¯å®Œå…¨ã§ã¯ãªã„ã“ã¨ãŒåˆ†ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ãŒã€å¯†åº¦æ³¢ç†è«–ãŒã©ã†ã„ã†ã‚‚ã®ã‹ã€ãã®ç‰¹å¾´ã‚’è‰¯ãæ‰ãˆã¦ã„ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‹ã‚‰ã€è‰¯ãå¼•ãåˆã„ã«å‡ºã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚</p>

<h2 id="å¯†åº¦æ³¢ç†è«–">å¯†åº¦æ³¢ç†è«–</h2>

<p>ã“ã“ã‹ã‚‰ã¯ã€å®Ÿéš›ã«å¯†åº¦æ³¢ã®åˆ†æ•£é–¢ä¿‚å¼ã‚’æ±‚ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã‚’è€ƒãˆã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
ã—ã‹ã—ä¸€èˆ¬çš„ãªéŠ€æ²³å††ç›¤ã®å‹•åŠ›å­¦ã«ã¯ã€æ•°å€¤è¨ˆç®—ãŒå¿…è¦ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ãã“ã§ã€ã“ã“ã§ã¯éŠ€æ²³å††ç›¤ä¸­ã‚’é‹å‹•ã™ã‚‹æ’æ˜Ÿç¾¤ã‚’æµä½“ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ‰±ã„ã€ãã®ã‚¬ã‚¹ã®åˆ†æ•£é–¢ä¿‚å¼ã‚’æ±‚ã‚ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã‚¬ã‚¹ã®é‹å‹•æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã¯</p>

\[\frac{\partial \mathbf{v}}{\partial t} + (\mathbf{v} \cdot \nabla) \mathbf{v} 
= - \frac{1}{\Sigma} \nabla P - \nabla \Phi \tag{4}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ã‹ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§\(\mathbf{v} = (v_R, v_\varphi)\)ã¯é€Ÿåº¦ãƒ™ã‚¯ãƒˆãƒ«ã€\(\Sigma\)ã¯è³ªé‡é¢å¯†åº¦ã€\(P\)ã¯æ’æ˜Ÿå††ç›¤ã‚’ã‚¬ã‚¹ã¨è¦‹ç«‹ã¦ãŸå ´åˆã®ç†±é‹å‹•ã«ã‚ˆã‚‹åœ§åŠ›ã€\(\Phi\)ã¯é‡åŠ›ãƒãƒ†ãƒ³ã‚·ãƒ£ãƒ«ã§ã™ã€‚
ã“ã®å¼ã®\(R\)æˆåˆ†ã¯</p>

\[\frac{\partial v_R}{\partial t} + v_R \frac{\partial v_R}{\partial R} + \frac{v_\varphi}{R} \frac{\partial v_R}{\partial \varphi} - \frac{v_\varphi^2}{R} 
= - \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial R} - \frac{1}{\Sigma} \frac{\partial P}{\partial R} 
= - \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (\Phi + h) \tag{5}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
é€”ä¸­ã€\(P = K \Sigma^\gamma\)ã‚’ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«çŠ¶æ…‹æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã¯ãƒãƒªãƒˆãƒ­ãƒ¼ãƒ—ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã€ã•ã‚‰ã«ã‚¨ãƒ³ã‚¿ãƒ«ãƒ”ãƒ¼\(h\)ã‚’</p>

\[h 
\equiv \int \frac{dP}{\Sigma (P)} 
\underbrace{=}_{dP = K\gamma \Sigma^{\gamma -1} d\Sigma} K \gamma \int \Sigma^{\gamma -2} d\Sigma 
= \frac{K\gamma}{\gamma -1} \Sigma^{\gamma -1} \tag{6}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«å®šç¾©ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚
åŒæ§˜ã«\(\varphi\)æˆåˆ†ã¯</p>

\[\frac{\partial v_\varphi}{\partial t} + v_R \frac{\partial v_\varphi}{\partial R} + \frac{v_\varphi}{R} \frac{\partial v_\varphi}{\partial \varphi} + \frac{v_R v_\varphi}{R} 
= - \frac{1}{R} \frac{\partial \Phi}{\partial \varphi} - \frac{1}{\Sigma R} \frac{\partial P}{\partial \varphi} 
= - \frac{1}{R} \frac{\partial}{\partial \varphi} (\Phi + h) \tag{7}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«éŠ€æ²³å††ç›¤ãŒç„¡é™ã«è–„ã„ã¨ä»®å®šã™ã‚‹ã¨ã€ãƒã‚¢ã‚½ãƒ³æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\nabla^2 \Phi 
= 4\pi G \Sigma \delta(z) \tag{8}\]

<p>ã®é–¢ä¿‚ãŒæˆã‚Šç«‹ã¡ã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
ã“ã“ã§å®šå¸¸è»¸å¯¾ç§°ãªå¹³è¡¡çŠ¶æ…‹ã‚’0æ¬¡ã¨ã—ã€ãã“ã«æ‘‚å‹•ã‚’åŠ ãˆãŸå ´åˆã®å¿œç­”ã‚’è€ƒãˆã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
å®šå¸¸è»¸å¯¾ç§°ã‚ˆã‚Šï¼„\(\frac{\partial}{\partial t} = \frac{\partial}{\partial \varphi} =0\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚
ãã—ã¦ã“ã®å¹³è¡¡çŠ¶æ…‹ã§ã¯ã€ç°¡å˜ã®ãŸã‚å††é‹å‹•\(v_R =0\)ã§ã‚ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚
å¹³è¡¡çŠ¶æ…‹ã®ç‰©ç†é‡ã«ã¯0ã®æ·»ãˆå­—ã‚’ã¤ã‘ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ã™ã‚‹ã¨ã€(5), (6), (8)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[-\frac{v_\varphi^2}{R} 
= -\frac{\partial}{\partial R} (\Phi_0 + h_0) \tag{9}\]

\[h_0 
= \frac{K\gamma}{\gamma -1} \Sigma_0^{\gamma -1} \tag{10}\]

\[\frac{\partial^2 \Phi_0}{\partial R^2} 
= 4\pi G \Sigma_0 \delta (z) \tag{11}\]

<p>æ¬¡ã«ã€æ‘‚å‹•é‡ã«1æ¬¡ã®æ·»å­—ã‚’ã¤ã‘ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚</p>

\[v_R 
= v_{R, 1} (R, \varphi, t), \quad
v_\varphi 
= v_{\varphi, 0} + v_{\varphi, 1}, \quad
h 
= h_0 + h_1, \quad
\Phi 
= \Phi_0 + \Phi_1, \quad
\Sigma 
= \Sigma_0 + \Sigma_1 \tag{12}\]

<p>ã‚ˆã‚Šã€(5), (9)å¼ã‹ã‚‰</p>

\[\frac{\partial v_{R, 1}}{\partial t} + v_{R, 1} \frac{\partial v_{R, 1}}{\partial R} + \frac{v_{\varphi, 0}+v_{\varphi, 1}}{R} \frac{\partial v_{R, 1}}{\partial \varphi} - \frac{(v_{\varphi, 0} + v_{\varphi, 1})^2}{R} 
= -\frac{\partial}{\partial R} (\Phi_0 + h_0 + \Phi_1 + h_1)\]

<p>ã§ã™ãŒã€æ‘‚å‹•é‡ã¯å¾®å°ãªã®ã§ã€ãã®2ä¹—ã‚’ç„¡è¦–ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ãã—ã¦(9)-(11)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\frac{\partial v_{R, 1}}{\partial t} + \Omega \frac{\partial v_{R, 1}}{\partial \varphi} - 2\Omega v_{\varphi, 1} 
= - \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (\Phi_1 + h_1) \tag{13}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ•´ç†ã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
é€”ä¸­ã€\(\Omega = v_{\varphi, 0} / R\)ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚
åŒæ§˜ã«(7)å¼ã¯</p>

\[\frac{\partial v_{\varphi, 1}}{\partial t} + v_{R, 1} \left\{ \frac{d}{d R} (R \Omega) + \Omega \right\} + \Omega \frac{\partial v_{\varphi, 1}}{\partial \varphi} 
= - \frac{1}{R} \frac{\partial}{\partial \varphi} (\Phi_1 + h_1) \tag{14}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§ã€æ‘‚å‹•é‡ã¯\(\varphi\)æ–¹å‘ã®ãƒ•ãƒ¼ãƒªã‚¨ãƒ¢ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã‚’è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
ã™ãªã‚ã¡æ‘‚å‹•é‡ã¯</p>

\[v_{R, 1} 
= v_{R, 1a} e^{i(m\varphi - \omega t)}, \quad 
v_{\varphi, 1} 
= v_{\varphi, 1a} e^{i(m\varphi - \omega t)}, \quad 
\Phi_1 
= \Phi_{1a} e^{i(m\varphi - \omega t)}, \quad 
h_1 
= h_{1a} e^{i(m\varphi - \omega t)}, \quad 
\Sigma_1 
= \Sigma_{1a} e^{i(m\varphi - \omega t)} \tag{15}\]

<p>ãªã©ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ã‘ã‚‹ã¨ã—ã€æŒ¯å¹…ã§ã‚ã‚‹\(v_{R, 1a}, v_{\varphi, 1a}, \Phi_1, h_1\)ã¯\(R\)ã®é–¢æ•°ã¨ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã™ã‚‹ã¨\(\frac{\partial}{\partial t} \rightarrow -i \omega, \frac{\partial}{\partial \varphi} \rightarrow im\)ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ãªã‚‹ãŸã‚ã€(13)å¼ã¯</p>

\[-i\omega v_{R, 1a} + im \Omega v_{R, 1a} - 2\Omega v_{\varphi, 1a} 
= - \frac{d}{dR} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) \tag{16}\]

<p>ãã—ã¦(14)å¼ã¯</p>

\[-i\omega v_{\varphi, 1a} + v_{R, 1a} \left\{\frac{d}{dR} (R\Omega) + \Omega \right\} + im \Omega v_{\varphi, 1a} 
= -\frac{im}{R} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a})
\tag{17}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§<a href="/galady/oort_constant#ã‚¨ãƒ”ã‚µã‚¤ã‚¯ãƒªãƒƒã‚¯è¿‘ä¼¼ã¨ã‚ªãƒ¼ãƒ«ãƒˆå®šæ•°">ã‚ªãƒ¼ãƒ«ãƒˆå®šæ•°\(B\)</a>ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã‚‹ã¨ã€\(\frac{d\Omega}{dR} + 2\Omega = -2B\)ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[v_{\varphi, 1a} 
= \frac{i}{\omega - m\Omega} \left\{ 2B v_{R, 1a} - \frac{im}{R} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) \right\} \tag{18}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã‚Œã‚’(16)å¼ã«ä»£å…¥ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\begin{align}
&amp;-i(\omega - m\Omega) v_{R, 1a} 
= \frac{2i\Omega}{\omega - m\Omega} \left\{ 2B v_{R, 1a} - \frac{im}{R} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) \right\} - \frac{d}{dR} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) \notag \\
&amp;\Longrightarrow \ 
-i \frac{(\omega - m \Omega)^2 + 4\Omega B}{\omega - m \Omega} v_{R, 1a} 
= \frac{2m \Omega}{R(\omega - m\Omega)} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) - \frac{d}{dR} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) \notag
\end{align}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
<a href="/galady/oort_constant#ã‚¨ãƒ”ã‚µã‚¤ã‚¯ãƒªãƒƒã‚¯è¿‘ä¼¼ã¨ã‚ªãƒ¼ãƒ«ãƒˆå®šæ•°">\(\kappa^2 = -4\Omega B\)</a>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ã€ã‚¨ãƒ”ã‚µã‚¤ã‚¯ãƒªãƒƒã‚¯æŒ¯å‹•æ•°ã‚’ç”¨ã„ã¦ã•ã‚‰ã«æ•´ç†ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[v_{R, 1a} 
= \frac{i}{\Delta} \left\{ (\omega -m \Omega) \frac{d}{dR} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) -\frac{2m\Omega}{R} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a})\right\} \tag{19}\]

<p>ã‚’å¾—ã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§\(\Delta \equiv \kappa^2 - (\omega -m\Omega)^2\)ã¨ã—ã¾ã—ãŸã€‚
ã“ã‚Œã‚’(18)å¼ã«ä»£å…¥ã™ã‚Œã°</p>

\[\begin{align}
v_{\varphi, 1a} 
&amp;= \frac{i}{\omega -m\Omega} \left[ \frac{2iB}{\Delta} \left\{ (\omega -m \Omega) \frac{d}{dR} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) -\frac{2m\Omega}{R} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a})\right\} - \frac{im}{R} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a})\right] \notag \\
&amp;= -\frac{1}{\Delta} \left\{2B \frac{d}{dR} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) - \left(\frac{4m\Omega B}{R (\omega - m\Omega)} + \frac{m\Delta}{R(\omega - m\Omega)}\right) (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) \right\} \notag \\
&amp;= -\frac{1}{\Delta} \left\{2B \frac{d}{dR} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) + \frac{m(\omega -m\Omega)}{R} (\Phi_{1a} + h_{1a}) \right\} \tag{20}
\end{align}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã‚‚ã—\(\omega\)ãŒå®Ÿæ•°ãªã‚‰ã€\(\Delta = 0\)ã¨ãªã‚‹åŠå¾„ãŒå­˜åœ¨ã—ã€(19), (20)å¼ãŒç™ºæ•£ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã®ã¨ã</p>

\[\omega - m\Omega 
= \pm \kappa \ \Longrightarrow \ 
\Omega_p 
\equiv \frac{\omega}{m} 
= \Omega \pm \frac{\kappa}{m} \tag{21}\]

<p>ã¨ãªã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã“ã§\(\Omega_p\)ã¯ãƒ‘ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒ³é€Ÿåº¦ã§ã™ã€‚
ã“ã‚Œã¯(3)å¼ã«ãŠã„ã¦ã€\(n = \mp 1\)ã¨ã—ãŸå ´åˆã«ç›¸å½“ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒã‚ã‹ã‚Šã¾ã™ã€‚
ã“ã®å ´åˆã¯å…±é³´ãŒç”Ÿã˜ã€å°ã•ãªæ“¾ä¹±ã‚’ç”¨ã„ãŸè§£æãŒç ´ç¶»ã—ã¾ã™ã€‚<br />
ã“ã“ã‹ã‚‰ã¯ã€å¯†åº¦åˆ†å¸ƒã®æ“¾ä¹±\(\Sigma_1\)ã«ã¤ã„ã¦æ±‚ã‚ã‚‹ã“ã¨ã«ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
(6)å¼ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\begin{align}
h_0 + h_1 
&amp;= \frac{K \gamma}{\gamma -1} (\Sigma_0 + \Sigma_1)^{\gamma -1} 
= \frac{K \gamma}{\gamma -1} \Sigma_0^{\gamma -1} \left( 1 + \frac{\Sigma_1}{\Sigma_0}\right)^{\gamma -1} 
\approx \frac{K \gamma}{\gamma -1} \Sigma_0^{\gamma -1} \left\{ 1+(\gamma -1) \frac{\Sigma_1}{\Sigma_0}\right\} \notag \\
&amp;= \underbrace{\frac{K \gamma}{\gamma -1} \Sigma_0^{\gamma -1}}_{(10)} + K \gamma \Sigma_1 \Sigma_0^{\gamma -2} 
\ \Longrightarrow \ 
h_1 
= K \gamma \Sigma_0^{\gamma -2} \Sigma_1 \tag{22}
\end{align}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚
ã•ã‚‰ã«çŠ¶æ…‹æ–¹ç¨‹å¼ã‹ã‚‰ã€éŸ³é€Ÿã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã—ã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚
ã™ã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[c_s^2 
= \frac{dP}{d\Sigma} 
= K \gamma \Sigma^{\gamma -1} \tag{23}\]

<p>ã‚ˆã‚Š(22)å¼ã¯</p>

\[h_1 
= c_s^2 \frac{\Sigma_1}{\Sigma_0} \tag{24}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ•´ç†ã•ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
ã‚¬ã‚¹ã®é€£ç¶šã®å¼ã¯</p>

\[\frac{\partial \Sigma}{\partial t} + \nabla \cdot (\Sigma \mathbf{v}) 
= 0 \tag{25}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«ä¸ãˆã‚‰ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
éæ‘‚å‹•é‡\(\Sigma_0\)ã¨æ‘‚å‹•é‡\(\Sigma_1\)ã«ã¤ã„ã¦è€ƒãˆã‚‹ã¨</p>

\[\frac{\partial \Sigma_0}{\partial t} + \nabla \cdot (\Sigma_0 \mathbf{v}_0) 
= 0 \tag{26}\]

\[\begin{align}
&amp;\frac{\partial}{\partial t} (\Sigma_0 + \Sigma_1) + \nabla \cdot \{ (\Sigma_0 + \Sigma_1) (\mathbf{v}_0 + \mathbf{v}_1) \} 
\approx \frac{\partial \Sigma_0}{\partial t} + \frac{\partial \Sigma_1}{\partial t} + \nabla \cdot \{ \Sigma_0 ( \mathbf{v}_0 + \mathbf{v}_1) \} + \nabla \cdot  ( \Sigma_1 \mathbf{v}_0 ) 
= 0 \notag \\
&amp;\underbrace{\Longrightarrow}_{(26)} \ \frac{\partial \Sigma_1}{\partial t} + \nabla \cdot (\Sigma_0 \mathbf{v}_1) + \nabla \cdot (\Sigma_1 \mathbf{v}_0) 
= 0 \tag{27}
\end{align}\]

<p>å††ç­’åº§æ¨™ã«ãŠã‘ã‚‹ç™ºæ•£ã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[\nabla \cdot (\Sigma_0 \mathbf{v}_1) 
= \frac{1}{R} \left\{ \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R \Sigma_0 v_{1R}) + \frac{\partial}{\partial \varphi} (\Sigma_0 v_{1\varphi}) + R \frac{\partial}{\partial z} (\Sigma_0 v_{1z})\right\} 
= \frac{1}{R} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R \Sigma_0 v_{1R}) + \frac{\Sigma_0}{R} \frac{\partial v_{1\varphi}}{\partial \varphi}\]

\[\nabla \cdot (\Sigma_1 \mathbf{v}_0) 
= \frac{1}{R} \frac{\partial}{\partial \varphi} (\Sigma_1 v_{0\varphi}) 
= \Omega \frac{\partial \Sigma_1}{\partial \varphi}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«è¨ˆç®—ã•ã‚Œã‚‹ãŸã‚ã€(27)å¼ã¯</p>

\[\frac{\partial \Sigma_1}{\partial t} + \Omega \frac{\partial \Sigma_1}{\partial \varphi} + \frac{1}{R} \frac{\partial}{\partial R} (R \Sigma_0 v_{1R}) + \frac{\Sigma_0}{R} \frac{\partial v_{1\varphi}}{\partial \varphi} 
= 0 \tag{28}\]

<p>ã®ã‚ˆã†ã«æ›¸ãæ›ãˆã‚‰ã‚Œã¾ã™ã€‚
