\[-i(\omega -m \Omega) \Sigma_1 + \frac{1}{R} \frac{d}{dR} (R \Sigma_0 v_{1R}) + \frac{im \Sigma_0}{R} v_{1\varphi} 
= 0 \tag{29}\]

